title: IAA Tonight | What Will It Take to Get Kevin Durant?
description: What should the asking price be for Kevin Durant? Brandon Marshall, LeSean McCoy, Ashley Nicole Moss and Antoine Walker discuss if it's more likely that Durant will be traded before the season, or will he be stuck on the Nets roster while they try to find a trade partner willing to give them everything they want. Plus, is Odell Beckham Jr. overhyped? One of our hosts believes so.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Brandon Marshall, LeSean McCoy, Ashley Nicole Moss, Antoine Walker)
